<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214889>
    bibo:endPage "88" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "83" ;
    bibo:volume "3484" ;
    dc:creator "Nadolny, Anton A.; Ponomarev, Alexandr V.; Dvadnenko, Konstantin V." ;
    dc:date "2012" ;
    dc:title "A new wolf spider species in the genus Alopecosa Simon, 1885 (Araneae: Lycosidae) from Eastern Europe" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214890>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214891>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214892>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214893> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214890>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 12. Habitus and copulatory organs of Alopecosa kovblyuki sp. nov. from Ukraine (2 – 5, 7 – 8 — TNU 2819 / 1; 5, 9, 12 — TNU 2814 / 1; 10 — TNU SO 70; 11 — TNU SO 49 / 2). 1 — male in natural habitat (Crimea, Lebyazh'i Islands); 2 — male pedipalp, ventral; 3 — male pedipalp, prolatero-ventral; 4 — bulbus, retrolateral; 5 – 6 — tegular (= median) apophysis, ventral (variation); 7 — embolic division, ventral; 8 — embolic division, prolatero-caudal; 9 – 11 — epigyne, ventral (variation); 12 — epigyne, dorsal. Abbreviations: AEP — anterior epigynal pocket; E — embolus; ED — embolic division; S — epigynal septum; Se — synembolus; TgA — tegular (= median) apophysis. Arrow indicates projection of tegulum. Scale bar: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/214890/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214891>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13 – 15. Male copulatory organs of Alopecosa kovblyuki sp. nov. and A. taeniopus from Russia (13 — ZMMU; 14 — CP 25.11.29 / 1) and A. taeniopus (15 — CP 25.11.5 / 34) from Russia. 13 — bulbus, ventral; 14 – 15 — bulbus, ventral (a little on front). Abbreviations: ED — embolic division; TgA — tegular (= median) apophysis. Arrow indicates projection of tegulum. Scale bar: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/214891/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214892>
    dc:description "FIGURE 16. Comparative phenology of Alopecosa kovblyuki sp. nov. and A. taeniopus based on specimens collected by pitfall traps in the environs of Solenoe Ozero Village, Crimea during 2009." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/214892/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214893>
    dc:description "FIGURE 17. Localities of Alopecosa kovblyuki sp. nov. (squares) in Ukraine and Russia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/214893/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

